Definition: criticize harshly or violently
Example: The press savaged the new President; The critics crucified the author for plagiarizing a famous passage
Synonyms: blast, pillory, crucify, criticize, harshly, or, violently, The, press, savaged, the, new, President, critics, crucified, author, for, plagiarizing, a, famous, passage
Frame: 8,9
Category: verb.communication
